  "text": "Tibia has complicated geometry and material properties. So obtaining trustable computer models of the bone has been major problem in modeled based researches. Thus most of researchers have simplified it considering it as a cylinder, defining one material and ignoring spongy bone and bone marrow in Models. Defining material of bone in software has been important in biomechanical behavior results [CITATION_1] .",
